=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
גּדל / gâdal / gaw-dal'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root; 
=== Verb ===
properly to [[twist]] (compare {{HH|1434}}), that is, to be (causatively make) large (in various senses, as in body, mind, estate or honor, also in pride): - advance, boast, bring up, exceed, excellent, be (-come, do, give, make, wax), great (-er, come to . . estate, + things), grow (up), increase, lift up, magnify (-ifical), be much set by, nourish (up), pass, promote, proudly [spoken], tower.